headline: TKO Group, HE Turki Alalshikh, Sela enter multi-year partnership
summary: HE Turki Alalshikh, together with TKO Group (TKO) Holdings, and Sela announced a multi-year partnership to establish a new boxing promotion that will provide a premier platform for both leading boxers and prospects in the sport. TKO will serve as managing partner, providing day-to-day operational expertise, management, and oversight of the promotion, with executive leadership anchored by UFC President and CEO Dana White and WWE President and TKO Board Member Nick Khan. Published first on TheFly
